data.description: The pool home you've been waiting for is here! Ready for the summer, and you can call it home. This home has been remodeled, so many things to list: New cabinets, appliances, flooring, water heater, air conditioner, bathrooms, and much more. You will notice from the time you step inside, open and comfortable. Nice brick fireplace add to the ambiance of this home. There's a screen patio out back overlooking the awesome pool, ready to make a splash!  Then there's also a 1 car garage and if that's not enough the seller is leaving the Maytag washer /dryer and the water softner system so you don't have to buy one. A must see home. New pool liner 2015, New roof 2009, New electric panel 2014, New plumbing 2014, New A/C 2017, New kitchen 2018, New water heater and water softener to be installed.
